Ordering the Data:

SELECT title,release_year,rental_rate
FROM film
ORDER BY release_year ASC, rental_rate DESC

GROUP BY: the average rental rate for each rating category.

SELECT AVG (rental_rate),rating
FROM film
GROUP BY rating

The Minimum and Maximum rental durations for each rating category.

SELECT MIN (rental_duration), MAX(rental_duration), rating
FROM film
GROUP BY rating
